<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿrftk yạ sydy
 ʿrftk ḥyn rạ̉ytk wsṭ ạllhyb
 wḥyn tṣạʿd ʿṭr ạlfdạʾ bkẖwrạaⁿ nqyạaⁿ zkyạaⁿ
 bnạr ạlṣlyb!
 ʿrftk
 ḥyn rạ̉ytk trnw ạ̹ly̱ ṣạlbyk..
 wtḥnw ʿlyhm bḥb ʿjyb!
 wqd dẖqt fy ạ̉rḍnạ jfwẗ
 wạnt ạlrqyq..
 wạ̉nt ạlwdyʿ..
 wạ̉nt ạlḥbyb</lyrics>
<title>ʿrftuka</title>
</song>